00:36:49,360 --> 00:36:50,520
Jangan menangis.

492
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:52,880
Kaki saya selalu terseliuh
semasa bermain bola.

493
00:36:52,960 --> 00:36:54,160
Tak apa-apa.

494
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:57,080
Sungguh?

495
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:57,760
Ya.

496
00:36:58,720 --> 00:37:00,440
Doktor, jangan begitu kuat.

497
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:03,840
Bahu terkehel juga.

498
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,560
Gu Fei Ming, awak bodoh ke?

499
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:09,600
Bahagian mana lagi yang tercedera?

500
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:11,040
Sini.

501
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,800
Tak apa-apa.

502
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,240
Adakah saya akan hilang ingatan?

503
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:19,000
Jangan risau, awak tak hilang ingatan.

504
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:20,560
Mungkin awak akan menghidapi demensia.

505
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,160
Baiklah.

506
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,400
Serahkan dia kepada awak.

507
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:24,280
Kami pergi dulu.

508
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,960
Awak rasa sakit di mana?

509
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:36,720
Qi Qi, awak dah maafkan saya?

510
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:39,440
Si bodoh.

511
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,400
Mengapa awak begitu bodoh?

512
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:04,520
Shan Shan, kenapa awak datang?

513
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:08,080
Pemeriksaan mengejut.

514
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,760
Masuklah.

515
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:29,800
Sudah lama awak tak makan masakan saya.

516
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:33,400
Biar saya tunjukkan kemajuan saya.

517
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,160
Boleh ke?

518
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:36,720
Jangan cederakan diri.

519
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:40,280
Awak perlu hantar saya ke hospital.

520
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:41,920
Jangan risau.

521
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,960
Saya dah baca berita di Internet.

522
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:59,720
Jangan salah faham.

523
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:02,040
Saya dan Sun Bin Yu tiada hubungan.

524
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:04,080
Mereka tulis sembarangan.

525
00:39:04,240 --> 00:39:05,160
Jangan percaya.

526
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,080
Saya tahu.

527
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,520
Saya tahu kamu tiada hubungan.

528
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:12,560
Saya datang tengok keadaan awak.
Awak tak apa-apa?

529
00:39:13,480 --> 00:39:14,160
Saya?

530
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,360
Saya tak apa-apa.

531
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:18,680
Mereka menyebarkan khabar angin saja.

532
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,720
Saya tak pedulikan mereka.

533
00:39:23,720 --> 00:39:24,640
Baguslah kalau begitu.

534
00:39:30,720 --> 00:39:31,760
Jangan buat lagi.

535
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,480
Tak boleh makan lagi.

536
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:43,480
[Berkenaan dengan berita palsu tentang]

537
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:46,120
[kehidupan peribadi Liang Chen,]

538
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,520
[syarikat kami akan]

539
00:39:48,680 --> 00:39:50,960
[mengambil tindakan undang-undang.]

540
00:39:51,120 --> 00:39:53,960
[Tolong jangan percaya khabar angin
atau sebarkan khabar angin.]


